Installing following plugins will make the work with your ~TiddlyWiki easier:

* [[Relink|https://flibbles.github.io/tw5-relink/]] - When renaming a tiddler, Relink can update the fields, filters, and widgets of all other tiddlers.
* [[Edit-CompText|https://snowgoon88.github.io/TW5-extendedit/]] - This plugin adds completion when editing the body of a tiddler.